In April, I will be opening a new tattoo studio here in Madison, Sleepy Reaper Tattoo, with some of my best friends and favorite artists, Lincoln Rust and Will Spencer. 
@lincolnrusttattoos @willdotattoos 
Please make sure to head over to our official Instagram page @sleepyreaperwi and give us a follow. It would also be a great help if you could share this post or the page to your story and friends. 
The shop will be located at 6000 Gisholt Drive, suite 104 in Monona, WI. Construction is happening now and we hope to be open to the public sometime next month. 
I am very excited to start this new chapter of my tattoo journey. It has been a long and paperwork filled road to get to where we are now and it is almost time for that hard work to pay off. 
If you saw my post last month about me postponing my books opening, this is what I was referring to. The official opening date is still up in the air but once that happens and we get our feet under us, I will make another announcement about my books opening. 
I wanted to take this opportunity to thank @mindflosstattoo for giving me the space to grow over the past 6 years. Mindfloss has been the only shop that I have worked at in Madison and it is such a bitter sweet feeling to leave but I am looking forward to what the future has in store.
I also want to thank @barber_tattoo_madison Madison for hosting me over my temporary transition period while I get the shop up and running. 
Here is to another chapter in my life!
Long live Sleepy Reaper!
@sleepyreaperwi
